<header><h2>Header内容区</h2></header>
<div class="container">
    <div class="middle"><h4>中间弹性区</h4></div>
    <div class="left"><h4>左边栏</h4></div>
    <div class="right"><h4>右边栏</h4></div>
</div>
<footer><h4>Footer内容区</h4></footer>
实现方法1：
  *{ margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    header{ width: 100%; height: 40px; background: red;}
    .container{
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 0 200px;/*利用父级元素设置左右内边距的值，把父级的三个子盒子往中间挤*/
    }
    .container .middle{
        float: left;
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        background: yellow;
    }
    .container .left{
        float: left;
        position: relative;
        left: -200px;
        width: 200px;
        height: 300px;
        background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 1);
        margin-left: -100%;/*左侧盒子到最左边*/
    }
    .container .right{
        float: right;
        position: relative;
        right: -200px;
        width: 200px;
        height: 300px;
        background: rgba(0,255,0,1);
        margin-left: -200px;
    }
    footer{ width: 100%; height: 40px; background: #333;}
    
方法2：
    *{ padding: 0; margin: 0; }
    header{ width: 100%; height: 40px; background: red;}
    .container{
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .container .middle{
        float: left;
        width: 100%;
        height: 300px;
        background: yellow;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        padding: 0 200px;
    }
    .container .left{
        float: left;
        width: 200px;
        height: 300px;
        background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 1);
        margin-left: -100%;/*左侧盒子到最左边*/
    }
    .container .right{
        float: right;
        width: 200px;
        height: 300px;
        background: rgba(0,255,0,1);
        margin-left: -200px;
    }
    footer{ width: 100%; height: 40px; background: #333;}
